# ==========================================
# AI IDE (Antigravity/Cursor) Ignore Rules
# 让底层检索系统 (ripgrep/fd) 自动忽略以下文件包，极大提升回答速度并降低幻觉错乱
# ==========================================

# ---- Binary & Large Files (二进制和大文件) ----
*.pdf
*.docx
*.doc
*.xls
*.xlsx
*.ppt
*.pptx
*.zip
*.rar
*.7z

# ---- Archive Folders (归档文件夹 - 不加入日常上下文) ----
归档/
归档*/
*归档/
*归档*/
archive/
Archive/

# ---- Extracted Textbook Folders (解压后的外部教材 - 太大) ----
货币、金融市场与金融机构*/

# ---- System Files ----
~$*
*.tmp
*.bak
Thumbs.db
.DS_Store

# ---- Editor Temp Files ----
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# ---- Office Lock Files ----
~$*.doc
~$*.docx
~$*.xls
~$*.xlsx
~$*.ppt
~$*.pptx

# ---- Agent Internal Cache ----
.agent/.cache/
.agent/.tmp/

# ---- Compilation & Build (如有前端开发拓展) ----
node_modules/
.npm/
